provisions.content:
23. Every plan and cross section of a roof truss for a span of over 31 feet
     shall be accompanied by an enlarged detail drawing of the truss showing-
          (a) all U straps;
          (b) threeway straps;
          (c) sizes of straps and bolts;
          (d) the method of anchoring every truss to a wall, pier, column or buttress.
